RuneScape: Dragonwilds is an open world survival game shaped by player feedback from alpha to launch and beyond. Our players help build and guide the roadmap - a living document that evolves with your input to make this adventure the best it can be. We can t wait!

The expansive continent of RSD.TOOLS remains uncharted, and what lies beyond the veil is still a mystery for now. Together, we'll uncover it's secrets.

RSD.TOOLS

RSD.TOOLS

RSD.TOOLS

Here you will find a suite of browser-based editors for Runescape Dragonwilds. The main tool is a visual Character Inventory Editor that lets you load your character save file, modify your inventory, and export the updated save. All without installing any software or mods.

Character

Item Editor

TEst on quests, level skills and wield runes to shape the world around you.

This tool will allow you complete control of your inventory. You can spawn in quest items you shouldn't have, add 1 million logs to your bag, equip the best weapons and armour on a fresh level 1. Its your game now.

Disclaimer: This tool will ruin the adventure of this game. You will become item god. Please enjoy the game first, back up your save, then modify your inventory to build the worlds largest castle.

LOOT DROP TABLES

REVEALED

What are the odds? Take a look. We know the numbers.

No estimates, no guessing, these drop tables are directly from the game files. View exactly who drops what and how often.

Hunt down that rare Shadowscale drop or Hoplite Shield with full confidence that your odds are 1%.

Learn Everything

Recipe Unlocker

Can't get that last vestige? We got you.

View all of the recipes and vestiges you've unlocked so far. We'll show you if you missed any, and unlock them for you, if you want.

This tool will allow you to craft everything and skip hunting rare drop tables. Use at the cost of your own fun.

Disclaimer: Back up your save. We won't stop you from unlocking things at level 1 that you shouldn't have.

But wait theres more

Tools on Tools

RSD.Tools is a collection of tools for Runescape Dragonwilds.

This is a free-to-use passion project of mine. I datamine the game, browse the files, find relevant and useful information. Then compile that information and create a tool with it. The tools featured on this page are what I think are the most useful. But there are many others, check them out!

The Spell Editor is pretty neat. It lets you play with the dev spells. The Character Editor is cool too. Set your hydration and hunger to never decay! But back up your save. Seriously, we don't know what will break. #SpaghettiCode

Dragons have awoken on RuneScape s forgotten continent of RSD.TOOLS. Stranded in this untamed land, you must gather resources, build shelters, and craft weapons to withstand the growing dragon threat. Only by mastering survival and unlocking ancient secrets can you hope to slay the Dragon Queen and reclaim RSD.TOOLS - alone or with up to 3 friends.

Register now for your chance to join the Alpha testing, where you can help us shape and define our new RuneScape game.
